AI-Native Founder Playbook Agent Skill is an independent open-source project.

It is based on an original synthesis of publicly available ideas from Anthropic's "The Founder's Playbook: Building an AI-Native Startup" and public Agent Skills documentation.

The original playbook, Claude name, and related marks belong to their respective owners. Source PDFs are included under docs/ for convenient reading and attribution. The reusable bilingual skill instructions, scripts, templates, and references are independent synthesis and avoid long verbatim excerpts.
